OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778605559
OL,3,CEnd of an era for the man who's
OL,4,Ctravelled 52 years on the same rail
OL,5,Croute
OL,7,FWatch: ITV Meridian's Juliette
OL,8,FFletcher met Steve on his final
OL,9,Fjourney.
OL,11,FA commuter, who's travelled the same
OL,12,Frail route every day for 52 years, has
OL,13,Fmade his last journey to work.
OL,15,FSteve McCulloch has journeyed between
OL,16,FWindsor and Eton Central to
OL,17,FMaidenhead, taking two trains for his
OL,18,Fprinting job every day since 1974.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
