PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778605559
OL,3,CEnd of an era for the man who's
OL,4,Ctravelled 52 years on the same rail
OL,5,Croute
OL,7,FBut when he turned 70 he decided to
OL,8,Fretire and Great Western Railway
OL,9,Fwanted to mark the occasion.
OL,11,FThey presented him with a plaque
OL,12,Fbearing his name, similar to those put
OL,13,Fon the side of trains, and a gift bag.
OL,15,FSteve said: "I'm not sure how to take
OL,16,Fit really. It's got to be done, I'm 70
OL,17,Fnow, and you can't go on forever.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778605559
OL,3,CEnd of an era for the man who's
OL,4,Ctravelled 52 years on the same rail
OL,5,Croute
OL,7,F"It's going to be a bit of a wrench to
OL,8,Fstop doing it every day, but I will
OL,9,Fhopefully travel, three times a week
OL,10,For so to somewhere fairly local"
OL,12,FOver the years he's collected
OL,13,Fsnapshots of his journey - and he's
OL,14,Fcertainly had some memorable moments.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
