PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778605559
OL,3,CEnd of an era for the man who's
OL,4,Ctravelled 52 years on the same rail
OL,5,Croute
OL,7,F"In the days of slam-doors stock I was
OL,8,Fsitting at the end of the train at
OL,9,FSlough and we moved away and somebody
OL,10,Fcame running up the side and through
OL,11,Fthe door and tried to climb in but
OL,12,Fstumbled. I had to grab them and pull
OL,13,Fthem in," he said.
OL,15,FTrain travel has changed significantly
OL,16,Fsince the 1970s with more
OL,17,Felectrification, the introduction of
OL,18,Fhigh speed trains, and digital
OL,19,Fsignalling.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
