FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1778605559
OL,3,CEnd of an era for the man who's
OL,4,Ctravelled 52 years on the same rail
OL,5,Croute
OL,7,FMian Sarwar, the Station Manager for
OL,8,FGWR, Slough and Maidenhead area, said:
OL,9,F"Steve's been travelling with us for
OL,10,Fover 50 years and to acknowledge his
OL,11,Ftravelling and his loyalty with us, it
OL,12,Fwas important to acknowledge him and
OL,13,Fmark this occasion very well. "
OL,15,FSteve says he has plans for his
OL,16,Fretirement. He wants to travel further
OL,17,Fand has been invited to go to India,
OL,18,Fbut he also hopes to explore the UK
OL,19,Fmore... by train of course.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
